text: Ðis syndon ðære anre higde landgemæro to Fleote.
Ærest up of ðære sæ on scypcumb.
Up ðonne on scypcumb on ðæne bydelæcer suðeweardne.
Of ðam bydelæcere up on ðæt slæd be suðan Dyrnanleage on gerihte to Berhamme.
Up ðonne on Berham suðeweardne on ðæne hricgweg.
Of ðam hricgwege norð on readan weg ufeweardne.
Of readan wege norð andlang hricges on bitun liege.
Of bitun liege west andlang weges on gerihte to Crymelhamme, up on ða dic on ðone herpoð.
West ðonne on herpoð of cumbweges heafod.
Adune ðanne on cumbweg on horegan ford.
Of horegan forde adune on strem on nyðeran Stanford.
Of nyðeran Stanforda norð be ðæs yrðlandes foton on gerihte to litegan hlosstede.
Of litegan hlosstede on hreodmæde lace on Axan.
Of Axan eft ut on sæ.
And seo mædræden beniðan dic betweonan cealdan lace and cullig.
